B. p Dng Kin Thc Numpy

1. Basic Numpy Operations

In[]:
item_weight = mart['Item_Weight'].to_numpy()

mean_weight = np.nanmean(item_weight)
median_weight = np.nanmedian(item_weight) 
std_weight = np.nanstd(item_weight) 

print("Mean Weight:", mean_weight)
print("Median Weight:", median_weight)
print("Standard Deviation of Weight:", std_weight)

Mean Weight: 12.857645184135976
Median Weight: 12.6
Standard Deviation of Weight: 4.643127630847946
Gii thch:
  • to_numpy(): Chuyn i ct 'Item_Weight' thnh mng numpy.
  • np.nanmean(): Tnh gi tr trung bnh ca mng, b qua cc gi tr NaN.
  • np.nanmedian(): Tnh gi tr trung v ca mng, b qua cc gi tr NaN.
  • np.nanstd(): Tnh lch chun ca mng, b qua cc gi tr NaN.

2. Handling Missing Values

In[]:
# Kim tra cc gi tr thiu trong 'Item_Weight'
missing_values = np.isnan(item_weight).sum()  # m s lng gi tr NaN trong mng
print("Number of missing values in 'Item_Weight':", missing_values)

# in cc gi tr thiu bng gi tr trung bnh (khng thay i d liu hin c)
item_weight_filled = np.where(np.isnan(item_weight), mean_weight, item_weight)
print("Missing values filled with mean.")

Number of missing values in 'Item_Weight': 1463
Missing values filled with mean.
Gii thch:
  • np.isnan(): Kim tra cc gi tr NaN trong mng.
  • np.where(): Thay th cc gi tr NaN trong mng bng gi tr trung bnh tnh c.

5. Data Normalization

In[]:
# Chun ha Min-Max ca 'Item_Visibility'
item_visibility = mart['Item_Visibility'].to_numpy()
min_visibility = np.min(item_visibility)
max_visibility = np.max(item_visibility)

normalized_visibility = (item_visibility - min_visibility) / (max_visibility - min_visibility)
print("Normalized Visibility:", normalized_visibility[:5])

Normalized Visibility: [0.04886645 0.05870508 0.05103696 0.         0.        ]
Gii thch:
  • np.min(): Tm gi tr nh nht trong mng.
  • np.max(): Tm gi tr ln nht trong mng.
  • Biu thc (item_visibility - min_visibility) / (max_visibility - min_visibility): p dng chun ha Min-Max cho cc gi tr trong mng.

D. p Dng Kin Thc Matplotlib - Data Visualization

In[]:
# Thit lp mi trng v biu 
%matplotlib inline
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

matplotlib.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (10, 10)
matplotlib.rcParams['font.size'] = 15

# V biu  histogram cho ton b cc ct trong dataset
mart.hist(figsize=(15, 15), edgecolor='black')
plt.show()
Gii thch:
  • %matplotlib inline: Thit lp hin th cc biu trc tip trong notebook.
  • matplotlib.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (10, 10): Thit lp kch thc mc nh ca cc biu l 10x10 inch.
  • matplotlib.rcParams['font.size'] = 15: Thit lp kch thc font ch mc nh l 15.
  • mart.hist(figsize=(15, 15), edgecolor='black'): V biu histogram cho ton b cc ct trong dataset, vi kch thc 15x15 inch v cnh mu en.

1. Biu Phn Phi Trng Lng Sn Phm (Item Weight Distribution)

  • startangle=140: Bt u v biu t gc 140 c b cc p hn.
  • plt.axis('equal'): m bo biu trn c v di dng hnh trn (khng b mo).

PHN TCH D LIU

D liu t b dataset 'Bigmart Sales' bao gm cc ghi chp giao dch ca mt ca hng bn l, vi tng cng 8523 dng v 12 bin. Cc bin ny bao gm cc thng tin v sn phm, ca hng, v doanh s bn hng. Vic phn tch d liu t dataset ny s gip chng ta c ci nhn tng quan v cc yu t nh hng n doanh s bn hng v chun b cho vic d on doanh s bn hng ca ca hng.

Phn tch d liu chun b cho vic d on doanh s bn hng ca mt ca hng

d on doanh s bn hng ca mt ca hng, chng ta cn thc hin cc bc phn tch d liu sau:

  1. Khm ph d liu (Data Exploration):

    • Kim tra cc gi tr b thiu v x l chng.
    • Tnh ton cc thng k m t c bn nh trung bnh, trung v, v lch chun cho cc bin s.
    • V cc biu phn phi hiu r hn v d liu.

  2. Phn tch mi quan h (Relationship Analysis):

    • S dng biu scatter plot phn tch mi quan h gia gi bn l ti a (Item MRP) v doanh s bn hng (Item Outlet Sales).
    • S dng biu box plot so snh doanh s bn hng theo loi sn phm (Item Type).
    • S dng biu bar plot phn tch s lng ca hng theo nm thnh lp (Outlet Establishment Year) v loi ca hng (Outlet Type).

  3. Chun ha v bin i d liu (Data Transformation and Normalization):

    • Chun ha cc bin s nh Item Visibility m bo d liu nm trong khong hp l.
    • Bin i cc bin s nh Item MRP gim thiu s nh hng ca cc gi tr ngoi l.

  4. To cc bin s mi (Feature Engineering):

    • To cc bin s mi t d liu hin c, v d nh to bin s tng hp t Item Weight v Item Visibility to ra ch s mi th hin s ni bt ca sn phm.

Li ch ca vic phn tch d liu vi Numpy, Pandas v Matplotlib

  1. Numpy:

    • Gip thc hin cc php ton nhanh chng v hiu qu trn cc mng d liu ln.
    • H tr tnh ton cc thng k m t c bn v nng cao.

  2. Pandas:

    • Cung cp cc cng c mnh m thao tc v x l d liu, t vic c, ghi d liu n vic x l cc gi tr b thiu, lc d liu, v nhm d liu.
    • Gip d dng khm ph v phn tch d liu vi cc phng thc tin li.

  3. Matplotlib:

    • Gip trc quan ha d liu mt cch sinh ng v d hiu thng qua cc biu a dng.
    • H tr to cc biu ty chnh ph hp vi cc nhu cu phn tch khc nhau.

Tm quan trng ca phn tch d liu

Phn tch d liu l mt bc quan trng trong qu trnh ra quyt nh da trn d liu. i vi mt Data Analyst, vic phn tch d liu mang li nhng li ch sau:

  1. Hiu r hn v d liu:

    • Gip khm ph v hiu r cc c im ca d liu, t pht hin ra cc vn v c hi tim nng.

  2. Xc nh cc yu t nh hng:

    • Gip xc nh cc yu t chnh nh hng n doanh s bn hng, t a ra cc quyt nh kinh doanh hp l v hiu qu.

  3. D on v ti u ha:

    • Gip chun b d liu cho cc m hnh d on, t d on chnh xc doanh s bn hng v ti u ha cc chin lc kinh doanh.

  4. Ra quyt nh da trn d liu:

    • Cung cp c s khoa hc cho vic ra quyt nh, gim thiu ri ro v tng cng hiu qu kinh doanh.

  5. Nng cao k nng v hiu sut lm vic:

    • Gip Data Analyst nng cao k nng phn tch v trc quan ha d liu, t ci thin hiu sut lm vic v ng gp tch cc vo s pht trin ca t chc.

Qua vic p dng cc cng c v k thut phn tch d liu, chng ta c th ti u ha quy trnh kinh doanh, d on chnh xc doanh s bn hng v a ra cc quyt nh kinh doanh hiu qu, gp phn vo s thnh cng ca ca hng v t chc.
